snippet.title: ParadiZe Project | Reveal Trailer
snippet.description:
Fight, Hack, and Survive! Alone or with friends, explore a mysterious open-world infested by zombies. Collect materials, craft weapons, and fight for your life. Learn to capture and hack zombies to assist in fighting, defending, or exploring. Welcome to Paradize!

#ParadiZeProject will be available on PC & consoles in 2023.
